what_failed: Regression (0.37x): Decorrelated EXISTS/NOT EXISTS subqueries into independent CTEs with DISTINCT keys and converted INTERSECT-like patterns to IN/NOT IN joins. Pre-filtered dimension tables into CTEs to reduce join cardinality early.
why_it_failed: Materialized a GROUP BY self-join (HAVING MIN() <> MAX()) on the entire fact table BEFORE applying date/address/call_center filters. The original query filters catalog_sales first via correlated EXISTS clauses, then checks warehouse conditions. Pre-materializing the unfiltered self-join creates a massive intermediate result the optimizer cannot cost-estimate correctly.
